 "name",                        "sex"
 "Sonja Lang",                  "Female"   ; Creator of the language.
 "jan Misali",                  "Male"     ; Famous Toki Ponan youtuber.
 "Jonathan Gabel",              "Male"     ; Creator of sitelen sitelen.
